<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
        <h1>About Coco</h1>
        <hr>
        <div class="row">

            <div class= "col-md-4">
                <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: '100%', alt: "profile image"  %>

                <div class="skills">
                    <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
                        <div class="skill">
                        <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
                        <div class="progress">
                            <div
                            class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped progress-bar-animated bg-success"
                            role="progressbar"
                            aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                            aria-valuemax="100"
                            style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                            ><%= skill.percent_utilized %>%</div>
                        </div>
                        </div>
                    <% end %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class= "col-md-8">
                <p class="lead">Software engineer experienced in Ruby on Rails, JavaScript, React.js, Redux, PostgreSQL, HTML, Canvas, MySQL, Git and CSS. I love innovation and technology and getting involved in my communities. 
                </p>
                <p class="lead">After a Master of Science in biotechnology, I've had a successful career in Intellectual Property. My work experiences have honed my communication skills with multi-cultural teams. My work involved constantly learning new technologies and delivering projects in a fast paced environment under strict deadlines.
                </p>
                <p class="lead">Ever since I had exposure to programming, I was hooked and I have been coding ever since. I like puzzles, patterns, and finding creative solutions to challenging problems. 
                </p>
                <p>
                    <button
                        class="btn btn-lg btn-primary"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#jobHistory"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controler="jobHistory"
                    >
                        Job History
                    </button>

                    <button
                        class="btn btn-lg btn-primary"
                        type="button"
                        data-toggle="collapse"
                        data-target="#education"
                        aria-expanded="false"
                        aria-controler="education"
                    >
                        Education
                    </button>
                    </p>

                    <p>
                    <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                        Job 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                        Job 2
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="collapse" id="education">
                        <div class="card card-block">
                        School 1
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                        School 2
                        </div>
                        <div class="card card-block">
                        School 3
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </p>

                <p class="lead">
                    <%= link_to 'Portfolio', portfolios_path, class: 'btn btn-lg btn-dark'  %>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>